---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 385
  - Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Crossing the Flood
  - 77
---
Shut out worldly sights from your mind with endeavour and the utmost
perseverance.  and cross the perilous ocean of woe. which is the
world, in the firm barque of your virtues.
